reviewText: Nothing about this film is quiet. Full of absolute bangers
awesome video!  Great compilation with with smooth transitions between shots.
Big air, technical tricks, insane talent, deep passion: get inspired!

With so much free web content out there it is easy to wonder why you should pay for a wakeboarding movie. However, this full-length feature is well worth the small price. There is nothing quite like shutting out the rest of the world and popping in a high-quality, professionally produced action sports film. The production, music and riding is top-notch. Stressing style and big air over technicality, this film will make you feel stoked and shred ready. Great pickup at a great price!
